âœ… **Account Management**: Create, update, and delete accounts  
âœ… **Transaction Handling**: Deposit, withdraw, and transfer money  
âœ… **Transaction History**: View past transactions with CSV export  
âœ… **Security Enhancements**:  
   - Hashed PIN storage  
   - Login attempt limit  
   - Auto session timeout  
âœ… **Dark/Light Mode Toggle**  
âœ… **Analytics Dashboard**: Visual spending trends  
âœ… **Help & Feedback Section**: FAQs and user feedback submission   

